---
title: Herby Pork Meatballs & Broccoli Risoni Salad  with Parmesan, Dill & Parsley Mayonnaise & Lemon
description: Tonight’s dinner is lean, mean and extra green! We’ve got juicy pork meatballs sitting on top of a hearty risoni salad flavoured with your favourite green veg and a generous squeeze of lemon for extra tang. All you need is a drizzle of creamy dill & parsley mayo to pull this masterpiece together.

